   "source": [
    "## How to set up your project repo to host a website in docs AND a folder of notebooks\n",
    "\n",
    "```\n",
    "PROJECT REPO \n",
    ".gitignore\n",
    "(venv)\n",
    "docs/\n",
    "    |\n",
    "    index.html\n",
    "     (and friends)\n",
    "pynotebooks/\n",
    "     |\n",
    "    projectNotebook1.ipynb      \n",
    "    \n",
    "\n",
    "```\n"
   ]
